MINI DESCRIPTION OF SYSTEM 22/1/95

sentence finding
--> triggered by (.|?|!)  and \n\n (paragraph) triggering.

tagging
--> from a list of function words

grammar
--> rudimentary (1) punctuation or (2) Content Word (CW) followed
by Function Word (FW) giving minor and major boundaries respectively.

transcriptions
--> Oxford dictionary, or NRL rules if that fails
additional syllabification based on sonority
missing stress assignment for NRL transcriptions.

stress assignment 
--> just stress everything that has primary lexical stress

pauses
--> based on punctuation mark only

durations
--> fixed, from a list

f0
--> from a simple set of patterns specified in terms of target
points
